.******************************************************************************
.* System         : ALL with screen painting                                  *
.*                                                                            *
.* Include Name   : SCRCKFLD.PBL                                              *
.*                                                                            *
.* Function       : Check if a display only field is to be displayed.         *
.*                                                                            *
.* Author         : Justin Coates                                             *
.*                                                                            *
.* Date Written   : 04/02/1992                                                *
.*                                                                            *
.* Parameters     : KEY5          item number to check for (right justified)  *
.*                                                                            *
.* Returns        : EXIT = 0      display the field                           *
.*                  CCOL & CVERT  display position                            *
.*                  EXIT = 1      don't display the field                     *
.*                                                                            *
.* Modifications  :                                                           *
.******************************************************************************
SCRCKFLD  MOVE      ONE,EXIT
          PACK      KEY20,PRGID,SCRID,KEY5,SP20
          CALL      RSSCPS2                 * check field positions file
          CALL      RKSCPS2
          BRANCH    OVRCD,SCCKFLD9          * end of file
.
          MATCH     PRGID,SCPSPID
          GOTO      SCCKFLD9 IF NOT EQUAL   * different program id
.
          MATCH     SCRID,SCPSSID
          GOTO      SCCKFLD9 IF NOT EQUAL   * different screen id
.
          MATCH     KEY5,SCPSITM
          GOTO      SCCKFLD9 IF NOT EQUAL   * item not on file
.
          MOVE      SCPSCOL,CCOL            * set up column
          MOVE      SCPSROW,CVERT           * set up row
          MOVE      ZERO,EXIT               * Desc on file. (Disp Desc)
.
SCCKFLD9  RETURN
+
